Liono looks over to Zardus "Sorry about that Zardus not to breach our treaty. 
All maximals this an order Attack the newcomers and them only until told to 
do otherwise clear. Zardus I'll work with my forces can you work with yours. 
If we can get them together we have a chance to Defeat shuko for good. 
Hellbeast you in or out."

Tigerhawk opens a relay channel to all maximals "Liono has ordered that all 
maximals are to stop firing on Alliance and Preds until told other wise all 
those 
who break the peace treaty will answer to me. Tigerhawk aims the main guns at 
Anubis and starts to fire at him.
